---
title: Tarieven 2026 | Fysiopraktijk Zeist
description: Actuele tarieven van Fysiopraktijk Zeist voor 2026. Fysiotherapie, FysioFitness en overige diensten. Veelal vergoed door uw zorgverzekeraar.
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ description }}" />
  <script src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js"></script>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,400&family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  <style>
    /* Hero */
    .page-hero { background: var(--teal); padding: 56px 0 48px; }
    .page-hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .page-hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); max-width: 600px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .breadcrumb { font-size: .8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .breadcrumb a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.55); }
    .breadcrumb a:hover { color: #fff; }
    /* Content */
    .tarieven-content { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 0 80px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px; }
    .tarieven-note { background: #fff; border-left: 4px solid var(--orange); border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0; padding: 18px 24px; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; }
    .tarieven-note strong { color: var(--dark); }
    .tarieven-block h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .tarieven-block .block-sub { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .tarieven-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: #fff; border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow); }
    .tarieven-table thead tr { background: var(--teal); color: #fff; }
    .tarieven-table thead th { padding: 12px 18px; text-align: left; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .tarieven-table thead th:last-child { text-align: right; }
    .tarieven-table tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-light); transition: background .15s; }
    .tarieven-table tbody tr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .tarieven-table tbody tr:hover { background: var(--teal-pale); }
    .tarieven-table tbody tr.row-warning { background: #FFF8F5; }
    .tarieven-table tbody tr.row-warning:hover { background: #FFEFE8; }
    .tarieven-table td { padding: 13px 18px; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--dark); }
    .tarieven-table td:last-child { text-align: right; font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal); white-space: nowrap; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .tarieven-table td.code { color: var(--gray); font-size: .8rem; }
    .tarieven-table td.warning-price { color: var(--orange); }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .tarieven-table td, .tarieven-table th { padding: 11px 12px; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Nav -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="container nav__inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav__logo">
      {{ general.name }}
      <span>Fysiotherapeut zonder verwijzing</span>
    </a>
    <ul class="nav__links">
      <li><a href="/#behandelingen">Behandelingen</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#afspraak">Afspraak maken</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#team">Team</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#blog">Blog</a></li>
      <li><a href="/shop">Shop</a></li>
      <li><a href="/#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav__actions">
      <a href="https://wa.me/{{ general.whatsapp }}" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:10px 18px;font-size:.85rem">💬 Afspraak maken</a>
    </div>
    <button class="nav__hamburger" id="menuBtn" aria-label="Menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
  <a href="/#behandelingen" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Behandelingen</a>
  <a href="/#afspraak" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Afspraak maken</a>
  <a href="/#team" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Team</a>
  <a href="/#blog" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Blog</a>
  <a href="/shop" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Shop</a>
  <a href="/#contact" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Contact</a>
  <a href="https://wa.me/{{ general.whatsapp }}" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:8px">💬 WhatsApp afspraak</a>
  <a href="tel:{{ general.phone }}" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:4px">📞 {{ general.phone }}</a>
</div>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › Tarieven 2026</p>
    <h1>Tarieven 2026</h1>
    <p>Onderstaande tarieven gelden voor patiënten zonder aanvullende verzekering of zonder contract tussen uw verzekeraar en onze praktijk.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Content -->
<main>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="tarieven-content">

      <div class="tarieven-note">
        <strong>Verzekerd?</strong> De meeste behandelingen worden (deels) vergoed vanuit uw aanvullende zorgverzekering. Twijfelt u? Neem contact op via <a href="tel:{{ general.phone }}" style="color:var(--teal)">{{ general.phone }}</a> — wij helpen u graag.
      </div>

      <div class="tarieven-note" style="border-left-color: var(--teal);">
        <strong>Let op:</strong> De eerste afspraak bestaat standaard uit een intake én een eerste behandeling van totaal 50 minuten.
      </div>

      <!-- Fysiotherapie -->
      <div class="tarieven-block">
        <h2>Fysiotherapie</h2>
        <p class="block-sub">Tarieven per behandeling, onderzoek of groepssessie</p>
        <table class="tarieven-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Omschrijving</th><th>Code</th><th>Tarief</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for item in tarieven.fysiotherapie %}
            <tr{% if item.warning %} class="row-warning"{% endif %}>
              <td>{{ item.omschrijving }}</td>
              <td class="code">{{ item.code }}</td>
              <td{% if item.warning %} class="warning-price"{% endif %}>€ {{ item.tarief }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- FysioFitness -->
      <div class="tarieven-block">
        <h2>FysioFitness</h2>
        <p class="block-sub">Abonnementen onder begeleiding van onze therapeuten — inclusief BTW</p>
        <table class="tarieven-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Omschrijving</th><th>Periode</th><th>Tarief</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for item in tarieven.fysiofitness %}
            <tr>
              <td>{{ item.omschrijving }}</td>
              <td class="code">{{ item.periode }}</td>
              <td>€ {{ item.tarief }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Overig -->
      <div class="tarieven-block">
        <h2>Overig</h2>
        <p class="block-sub">Aanvullende diensten</p>
        <table class="tarieven-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Omschrijving</th><th></th><th>Tarief</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for item in tarieven.overig %}
            <tr>
              <td>{{ item.omschrijving }}</td>
              <td class="code">{{ item.code }}</td>
              <td>€ {{ item.tarief }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Orthomoleculair -->
      <div class="tarieven-block">
        <h2>Orthomoleculair</h2>
        <p class="block-sub">Externe praktijk — tarieven excl. BTW</p>
        <table class="tarieven-table">
          <thead><tr><th>Omschrijving</th><th></th><th>Tarief</th></tr></thead>
          <tbody>
            {% for item in tarieven.orthomoleculair %}
            <tr>
              <td>{{ item.omschrijving }}</td>
              <td class="code">{{ item.code }}</td>
              <td>€ {{ item.tarief }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer__grid">
      <div class="footer__brand">
        <div class="nav__logo">{{ general.name }}<span>Fysiotherapeut zonder verwijzing</span></div>
        <p>Wij behandelen de oorzaak van uw klacht — met persoonlijke aandacht en bewezen methoden. Al meer dan 35 jaar de fysiotherapiepraktijk van Zeist en omstreken.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
          <a href="https://wa.me/{{ general.whatsapp }}" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:10px 18px;font-size:.85rem">💬 WhatsApp</a>
          <a href="tel:{{ general.phone }}" style="padding:10px 18px;font-size:.85rem;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);border-radius:50px">📞 {{ general.phone }}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer__col">
        <h4>Openingstijden</h4>
        <ul class="footer__hours">
          <li><span>Maandag</span><span>{{ hours.monday }}</span></li>
          <li><span>Dinsdag</span><span>{{ hours.tuesday }}</span></li>
          <li><span>Woensdag</span><span>{{ hours.wednesday }}</span></li>
          <li><span>Donderdag</span><span>{{ hours.thursday }}</span></li>
          <li><span>Vrijdag</span><span>{{ hours.friday }}</span></li>
          <li><span>Zat &amp; Zon</span><span>Gesloten</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer__col">
        <h4>Contact</h4>
        <ul class="footer__links">
          <li>{{ general.address }}</li>
          <li style="margin-top:10px"><a href="tel:{{ general.phone }}">📞 {{ general.phone }}</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://wa.me/{{ general.whatsapp }}">💬 WhatsApp</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:{{ general.email }}">✉ {{ general.email }}</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer__bottom">
      <span>© 2026 {{ general.name }} — BIG-geregistreerd · {{ general.review_score }}/10 op ZorgkaartNederland</span>
      <div class="footer__legal">
        <a href="/veelgestelde-vragen">FAQ</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/algemene-voorwaarden">Algemene voorwaarden</a>
        <a href="/tarieven" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)">Tarieven 2026</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<a class="fab" href="https://wa.me/{{ general.whatsapp }}?text=Hallo%2C%20ik%20wil%20graag%20een%20afspraak%20maken" aria-label="WhatsApp">💬</a>

<script>
  const menuBtn = document.getElementById('menuBtn');
  const mobileMenu = document.getElementById('mobileMenu');
  menuBtn.addEventListener('click', () => mobileMenu.classList.toggle('open'));
  function closeMobileMenu() { mobileMenu.classList.remove('open'); }
  if (window.netlifyIdentity) {
    window.netlifyIdentity.on('init', user => {
      if (!user) { window.netlifyIdentity.on('login', () => { document.location.href = '/admin/'; }); }
    });
  }
</script>
</body>
</html>
